import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-recipe-page',
  templateUrl: './recipe-page.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['./recipe-page.page.scss'],
})
export class RecipePagePage implements OnInit {

  constructor() { }

  ngOnInit() {
  }

}
<ion-header [translucent]="true">
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>recipePage</ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content [fullscreen]="true">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large">recipePage</ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>

  <ion-list>
    <ion-list>
      <ion-item>
        <ion-input label="Recipe name" placeholder="Ex. chicken sandwich"></ion-input>
      </ion-item>
      <ion-item>
        <ion-select label="Default label" placeholder="Favorite Fruit">
          <ion-select-option value="apple">Apple</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="banana">Banana</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="orange">Orange</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option label="Recipe name">Custom</ion-select-option>
        </ion-select>
      </ion-item>
      </ion-list>
      </ion-list>

</ion-content>
